<%- include('partials/landing/head', {
    pageTitle: 'Privacy Policy – Qwint Caption by Qwintsoft LLP',
    pageDescription: 'Privacy Policy for Qwint Caption. We are committed to protecting your personal data.',
    robots: 'noindex, follow',
    extraCssPath: '/assets/css/landing-pages.css'
}) %>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/landing/navbar') %>

        <main class="subpage-main">
            <div class="subpage-wrap">
                <article class="subpage-card legal-page">
                    <a href="/" class="legal-back">← Back to Home</a>
                    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p class="legal-date">Last updated: February 19, 2025 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective: February 19, 2025</p>

                    <p>Qwintsoft LLP ("we," "us," "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy
                        explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your choices regarding your information
                        when you use Qwint Caption ("the Software") and our website.</p>

                    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p><strong>Account and Purchase Information:</strong> When you purchase Qwint Caption, Razorpay
                        collects
                        your name, email address, and payment information on our behalf. We receive a transaction record
                        that includes your email and purchase details we never see your full card number.</p>

                    <p><strong>License Activation Data:</strong> We store your license key, activation status, machine
                        identifiers (hashed), and usage credit balance to validate your license and track credit
                        consumption.</p>

                    <p><strong>Audio Processing Data:</strong> When you generate captions, audio segments from your
                        Premiere
                        Pro timeline are sent securely to our AI transcription service for processing. These audio
                        segments
                        are <strong>not stored</strong> beyond the duration required to complete transcription
                        (typically
                        seconds). We do not retain your audio content.</p>

                    <p><strong>Usage Analytics:</strong> We collect anonymous usage metrics (e.g., features used, credit
                        consumption, plugin version) to improve the Software. This data cannot be used to identify you
                        personally.</p>

                    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>To deliver the license key and activation instructions to your email</li>
                        <li>To validate your license and manage your credit balance</li>
                        <li>To process AI transcription requests</li>
                        <li>To send important product updates or security notices (not marketing spam)</li>
                        <li>To improve the Software and fix bugs</li>
                        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes. We
                        share
                        data only with:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Razorpay:</strong> For secure payment processing (governed by Razorpay's Privacy Policy)
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>OpenAI / Whisper AI:</strong> Audio is sent for transcription, not retained
                            post-processing</li>
                        <li><strong>Email service provider:</strong> For transactional emails (license delivery,
                            receipts)
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Legal authorities:</strong> Only when required by law</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
                    <p>We retain your account and license data for the duration of your license plus 3 years for legal
                        and
                        accounting purposes. You may request deletion of your data at any time (see Section 7). Audio
                        content processed for captioning is not retained.</p>

                    <h2>5. Security</h2>
                    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including TLS encryption for data in transit,
                        hashed
                        machine identifiers, and access controls on our databases. Payment data is handled entirely by
                        Razorpay's PCI DSS compliant infrastructure.</p>

                    <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
                    <p>Our website uses minimal cookies necessary for functionality (e.g., session management). We do
                        not
                        use tracking cookies for advertising. You may disable cookies in your browser settings, though
                        this
                        may affect website functionality.</p>

                    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
                        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
                        <li>Data portability</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@qwintsoft.com"
                            style="color:var(--clr-primary)">privacy@qwintsoft.com</a>. We will respond within 30 days.
                    </p>

                    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>Qwint Caption is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from
                        children.
                        If you believe we have inadvertently collected data from a child, please contact us immediately.
                    </p>

                    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes via
                        email
                        or in-app notification. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when the
                        policy
                        was last revised.</p>

                    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>For privacy-related questions or concerns, contact us at:<br />
                        <strong>Qwintsoft LLP</strong><br />
                        Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@qwintsoft.com"
                            style="color:var(--clr-primary)">privacy@qwintsoft.com</a>
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/landing/footer') %>
        <script src="/assets/js/landing.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
